data.description: Assumable Loan with 5.25% interest rate! This stunning Eagle Harbor residence has been tastefully updated, ensuring a fresh and modern living experience. Step inside and be greeted by the warm glow of new lighting, illuminating the beautiful interior. The home boasts new flooring throughout, providing a stylish and comfortable atmosphere. The kitchen is complete with ALL NEW BOSCH appliances, new backsplash and new lighting, creating a perfect blend of style and functionality. Rest easy knowing that you have a new roof (2021), HVAC (2022) & Water heater (2022), offering peace of mind and energy efficiency. The backyard offers a private oasis with abundant nature, including cardinals, hummingbirds, and owls that can all be enjoyed from the comfort of the extra-large fully screened lanai. Whether you are hosting a barbecue or sipping your morning coffee, this space offers the ideal setting to soak in the beauty of your surroundings. Eagle Harbor boasts a top-notch golf course, perfect for honing your skills or enjoying a leisurely round with friends. Stay active and challenge yourself on the tennis courts or pickleball courts, offering endless opportunities for friendly competition. Let the kids enjoy the excitement of the splash pad, providing fun under the sun.  Eagle Harbor amenities are some of the best in the area. Don't miss out on this opportunity to live a life of comfort, convenience, and endless recreation!
